mongo mongodb://dba_adm:*******@mongodb0.example.com:27017/?authSource=admin

where:

dba_adm is the user
****** is the password
mongodb0.example.com is the host
27017 is the port
authSource is the database with the user's credential
The default port for mongod is 27017.






mongo --host=localhost --port=27017 --username=db_admin --password='*********' --authenticationDatabase=playground